## Best Practices

- ✅ Add metadata to all pages
- ✅ Use dynamic metadata for dynamic pages
- ✅ Include OpenGraph tags
- ✅ Optimize meta descriptions (150-160 chars)
- ❌ Don't duplicate titles
- ❌ Don't skip alt text for images

